fulltitle: Ted Greene Guitar Lesson - Manhã de Carnaval
title: Ted Greene Guitar Lesson - Manhã de Carnaval
description:
RARE video footage. Ted Greene gives a guitar lesson covering the most popular song Manhã de Carnaval by Brazilian composers Luiz Bonfá and Antonio Maria.
Video Credits: Nick Stasinos 1/16/97 

My Life with The Chord Chemist: A Memoir of Ted Greene, Apotheosis of Solo Guitar by Barbara Franklin - Available at amazon.com
